{"tid":14131,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唉!我好撚灰想係大厦天台跳落去!!","createTime":"2016-11-30T11:18:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T15:43:10.000Z","uid":38631,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c8312cee884e32eb02de16bb8d8c3d942cb666","tid":14131,"uid":38631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:18:24.000Z","msg":"我去到邊都累人累物 唔死都冇用 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n創作強有咩用 做人屎就冇鬼用啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇用啦 冇近幫到我啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你知唔知  我由細到大好想生生性性做人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我做唔到呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係做唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿媽細細個就走左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿爸從來都唔理我  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你知唔知我係香港咁多年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係過得幾唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幾咁寂寞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有錢又點 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我一啲都唔開心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我果時己經諗 咁様做人一啲意義都冇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不如死左佢好過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246015d03ecc04134e268a47270ffd2e56cd9eea","tid":14131,"uid":2507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:19:22.000Z","msg":"唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"819e14a513c538109d2ce105c2cf52c16ab2139a","tid":14131,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:19:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}